117
00:07:39,480 --> 00:07:40,070
Deputy Chief Yan.

118
00:07:40,480 --> 00:07:41,000
Scholar Feng.

119
00:07:41,720 --> 00:07:42,320
Scholar Guan.

120
00:07:43,000 --> 00:07:44,670
